VALIDATION_SCHEMA:
{
  "definitions": {},
  "$schema": "http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#",
  "$id": "http://example.com/root.json",
  "type": "array",
  "title": "The Root Schema",
  "items": {
    "$id": "#/items",
    "type": "object",
    "title": "The Items Schema",
    "required": [
      "employeeNumber",
      "tripNumber",
      "ticketRequestNumber",
      "ticketAction",
      "ticketStatus",
      "remarks",
      "refDate",
      "orderId",
      "amount"
    ],
    "properties": {
      "employeeNumber": {
        "$id": "#/items/properties/employeeNumber",
        "type": "string",
        "title": "The Employeenumber Schema",
        "default": "",
        "examples": [
          "00081128"
        ],
        "minLength": 1,
        "pattern": "^(.*)$"
      },
      "tripNumber": {
        "$id": "#/items/properties/tripNumber",
        "type": "string",
        "title": "The Tripnumber Schema",
        "default": "",
        "examples": [
          "320"
        ],
        "minLength": 1,
        "pattern": "^(.*)$"
      },
      "ticketRequestNumber": {
        "$id": "#/items/properties/ticketRequestNumber",
        "type": "string",
        "title": "The Ticketrequestnumber Schema",
        "default": "",
        "examples": [
          "1644"
        ],
        "minLength": 1,
        "pattern": "^(.*)$"
      },
      "ticketAction": {
        "$id": "#/items/properties/ticketAction",
        "type": "string",
        "enum": [
          "C",
          "R",
          "P",
          "N"
        ],
        "title": "The Ticketaction Schema",
        "default": "",
        "examples": [
          "C"
        ],
        "minLength": 1,
        "pattern": "^(.*)$"
      },
      "ticketStatus": {
        "$id": "#/items/properties/ticketStatus",
        "type": "string",
        "enum": [
          "C",
          "G",
          "J",
          "W",
          "L",
          "K",
          "X",
          "Y",
          "A"
        ],
        "title": "The Ticketstatus Schema",
        "default": "",
        "examples": [
          "C"
        ],
        "minLength": 1,
        "pattern": "^(.*)$"
      },
      "remarks": {
        "$id": "#/items/properties/remarks",
        "type": "string",
        "title": "The Remarks Schema",
        "default": "",
        "examples": [
          "Cancellation remark"
        ],
        "minLength": 1,
        "pattern": "^(.*)$"
      },
      "refDate": {
        "$id": "#/items/properties/refDate",
        "type": "string",
        "title": "The Refdate Schema",
        "default": "",
        "examples": [
          "2019-04-13"
        ],
        "minLength": 1,
        "pattern": "^(.*)$"
      },
      "orderId": {
        "$id": "#/items/properties/orderId",
        "type": "string",
        "title": "The Orderid Schema",
        "default": "",
        "examples": [
          "7987987"
        ],
        "minLength": 1,
        "pattern": "^(.*)$"
      },
      "amount": {
        "$id": "#/items/properties/amount",
        "type": "integer",
        "title": "The Amount Schema",
        "default": 0,
        "examples": [
          1000
        ]
      }
    }
  }
}
